com.planbase.pdf.layoutmanager

Class XyDim

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.planbase.pdf.layoutmanager.XyDim

  • public class XyDim
extends Object
    Represents a 2D dimension in terms of X and Y where both X and Y must be non-negative. Do not confuse a dimension (measurement) with an XyOffset which represents coordinates where negative y is down from the upper left-hand corner.
